articles.author: Reuters
articles.title: Jack Black's Tenacious D band cancels Australia tour after comments on Trump shooting - Reuters
articles.description: American comedy-rock duo Tenacious D, formed by actors Jack Black and Kyle Gass, suspended the rest of its Australian tour after comments made by Gass over the assassination attempt on former U.S. President Donald Trump.

articles.title: Singer checks into rehab after viral national anthem performance - Good Morning America
articles.description: Ingrid Andress is apologizing for a now-viral performance of the national anthem at the 2024 Home Run Derby on Monday.
articles.content:
